          21... Rae8 22. c4 d4)
        13... Qxb5 {this time, black wins material by trading down}
        14. Nxd4
         (14. Qxb5 Nxb5)
        14... Qxc4 15. bxc4 Nxd4 16. c3 Nc2+ 17. Kd1 Nxa1 18. cxb4)
      12... Nf3+ 13. Kd1 N5d4 14. Nxd4 Nxd4)
